values:
I went to rickys house tonight with cassandra and jed
we had a good time i think 
i drove over to jeds house to pick her up and she kept me waiting almost 30 minutes. that was a drag. when she was finally finished and got in thje car we went to popeyes to grab some food. we met cass there. after we stuffed our faces we got back in the car and drove about 45 minutes to rickys house. some other people were there but i have no idea who they were. they werepretty stuck up. good hting they didnt stay for long.
i left around 1am and im here all snug in my pjs

im sure some would consider today a waste but to me it was pretty fun
all i did was relax in my pajamas and watch tv
it was nice to stay home for once
lately ive just been going out every single night
driving around with people and doing nothing
after relaxing from the time i woke up till after i dinner, i stopped by the strip and picked up a few cds and some clothes
nothing to exciting

i was probably the only person in the world without one of these things
im not sure what to write so ill just write what ive been thinking about
john is a liar
i dont even know why i even bothered with him
he has no consideration for anybody but himself and its appaling
i wish hed just disappear of the face of this earth
what
ill write more when i get the hang of this doohickey
im going to find some friends with common interests
buhbye
